# Agent Rules

This directory contains OMP agent rules that are automatically loaded when conditions match.

## Rule Format

Each rule file uses YAML frontmatter followed by markdown:

```markdown
---
description: Short description of what this rule does
condition: When this rule should be applied
---

Rule content in markdown...
```

## Fields

- `description` (required): What the rule enforces
- `condition` (required): When the rule is activated
- `ttsrTrigger` (optional): Time-to-suggest-trigger for proactive rule suggestions

## Adding Rules

Create a new `.md` file in this directory. OMP loads all rule files and applies them when their conditions match the current context.
